{"tid":2058732,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"去年針對法官行為的投訴無一證明屬實或部分屬實","createTime":"2020-06-10T11:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T11:37:29.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d037611587d8e6b6bb33519fc63a536ff437b334","tid":2058732,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1531328_1_L_20200610192515.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1531328_1_L_20200610192515.jpg&h=4ab1c332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗引述司法機構表示，去年司法機構處理368宗針對法官及司法人員的投訴中，沒有涉及法官行為的投訴證明屬實或部分屬實。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531328-20200610.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531328-20200610.htm&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVawKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=4b78c8c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531328-20200610.htm&h=5843d9a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531328-20200610.htm</a>"}]}